verbose_text: In addition to the articles supporting the use of Enzastaurin, AZD1152 or AZD1480 in anti-GBM therapy, our data provide biomarkers (the level of pH3T6, pH3S10 and pH3Y41) for the patient stratification having the most probabilities to reply to anti-GBM treatment including the Enzastaurin, AZD1152 and/or AZD1480 drugs.
